## 3. Difference between synchronous and asynchronous execution?

| Synchronous | Asynchronous |
|-------------|--------------|
| Immediate execution | Background execution |
| User waits | User continues working |

---

## 4. Why do enterprise systems use background jobs?
To handle heavy processing without slowing the system.

---

## 5. Why should developers think about scalability?
To ensure the system can handle increasing users and data.

---

## 6. Why are test cases important?
They verify that all features work correctly.

---

## 7. What happens when systems fail partially?
