---

## 8. Why do large systems require reliability engineering?
To ensure continuous and stable system performance.

---

## 9. Why should enterprise software avoid blocking operations?
Because it slows user experience and reduces performance.

---

## 10. Why is enterprise software different from small scripts?
Because it must handle large-scale users, data, and complex business logic.

